%vlocity_namespace%__Formula__c: IF(%WithQuote%, IF(%MedicalCoverage:EnrollInMedical% LIKE "Yes", true, IF(AND(%CoverageOptions% LIKE "Medical", %MedicalCoverage:EnrollInMedical% = null),true,false)), IF(%MedicalCoverageNQ:EnrollInMedicalNQ% LIKE "Yes", true, IF(AND(%CoverageOptions% LIKE "Medical", %MedicalCoverageNQ:EnrollInMedicalNQ% = null),true,false)))
